{"title":"分数问题","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1278","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span style=\"\">给出一个有n位有效数字的小数r。r所在区间是[0,1).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"\">让你求一个分母最小的分数,该分数化成小数四舍五入保留n位有效数字后为r。你只要输出分母的大小即可。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\">输入含有若干行,每行一个整数n和一个含有n位有效数字的小数r。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">输出若干行，每行一个解，表示最小的分母。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\">2 0.33<br>3 0.316</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\">3</span><br><span style=\"\">19</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>数据范围 1&lt;=n&lt;=15   0&lt;=r&lt;1</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>样例说明 1/3 化成小数保留2位小数位 0.33</p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}